            <div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">                
                
                <p n="1">
                    Prosperity! Fortune!
                </p>
                <p n="1-2">
                    Door-guardian brought by the lord king Vijayarājendra after destroying Kalyāṇapuram.
                </p>
                
